{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "失落的龙约 第26章 3-1 可能性的枷锁",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "战况僵持不下，一行寄希望于\\n王子和巫女前去与贝维特展开决战。\\n王子与贝维特对可能性的认识截然相反。\\n为了否定世界的一切，\\n贝维特释放了曾经吸收的魔神之力。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "唔……又是别的世界的我……\\n如此可就没完没了了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210177_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "不管再来多少都没关系，\\n我永远都愿为了亲爱的而战！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210177_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "如果我输给了异界的自己，\\n那就相当于否定了\\n亲爱的为我做过的一切。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210177_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我决不会让这种事情发生！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "是啊……不过，绯龙啊，\\n你也不必如此冲动。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210131_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "我们拥有原初之力，\\n自然不会败给未能觉醒的他们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210177_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "没错……能够得到原初之力\\n也都是多亏了亲爱的。\\n异界的我们还真是蠢到家了呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210177_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我如今的姿态正是\\n亲爱的与我爱的证明！\\n你们给我看清楚了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "虽然明白你们迟早会坚持不住……\\n不过我等得有些烦躁了……\\n再多唤来一些一举消灭你们好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "可恶，果然不想办法解决那家伙的话，\\n我们没法摆脱现在的这个泥潭……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "可敌人数量众多，\\n我们也不知道什么时候\\n才能杀到他身前。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_13"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "但如果不强行突破解决根本问题的话，\\n我们这样就只是在白白消耗体力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "各位……能否帮我一个忙。\\n我——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "没问题。\\n我一定会帮你杀出一条\\n通向那家伙的血路。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不用你说我们也明白。\\n我可没笨到现在还猜不透你的想法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "去吧，尤蒂尔。\\n和你的哥哥做个了断。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_11"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我们一定会为尤蒂尔\\n创造机会。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "大家……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_13"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "交给我们吧。\\n大家一起上！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_09",
                "100003_07",
                "100004_11"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伙伴们",
            "context": "好！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "去吧，尤蒂尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢谢大家！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_11"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "塞西娅你们也去吧！\\n对抗贝维特需要巫女的力量！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "好的！谢谢大家！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "贝维特哥哥！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "真是一群难缠的家伙……\\n怎么就是不能明白\\n根本不存在可能性这种东西呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "为什么！？\\n告诉我，贝维特哥哥！\\n为什么你如此讨厌可能性！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "告诉你又能如何？\\n事已至此，你还觉得\\n你能与我产生共鸣吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "还是说你以为\\n能靠你的嘴炮说服我？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "事到如今，\\n我自然明白你我少不了一战。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但我还是想要知道为什么。\\n因为那是我与哥哥\\n之间唯一值得信赖的联系……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "联系、信赖……又来这套！\\n信赖信赖信赖，\\n你除了这个还能说点别的吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "你还没看够吗！\\n那无数可能性的世界之中，\\n你那所谓的信赖究竟有什么下场！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "为什么看了这些你还是不能醒悟！\\n你明明已经被那些可能性给否定了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "可能性救不了任何人！\\n可能性只会带来绝望！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不。\\n我如今能够站在这里，\\n正是可能性所带来的奇迹。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "你说什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "也许大多数的世界里我都背叛了大家。\\n也许大多数的世界里我都抛弃了伙伴，\\n毁灭了世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那些都是谁都不希望看到的绝望世界。\\n但是……仍然有着\\n不会变成那样的可能性。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那就是我！\\n站在这里的我正是\\n存在着那种可能性的证据！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "是吗……\\n我终于明白你的本质了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "你不过是一个被可能性\\n所束缚的可悲的傀儡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你、你说束缚！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "为什么你始终不能明白！？\\n可能性会剥夺人们的自由！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "剥夺……自由？\\n你到底在说些什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "“人必须要有一番作为”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "“想要成为这样或那样的人”……\\n欲望让人们寄希望于可能性。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "只要没有欲望，就不需要可能性。\\n不，应该说正是有了可能性，\\n人们才有会各种欲望。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "可能性诱惑着人们渴望去得到，\\n迫使着人们走向既定的路线……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "我曾经什么都不想要，\\n虚无曾经是我的一切。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "然而可能性却蛊惑着我，\\n诱惑着我去追求我所没有的东西，\\n迫使我去有一番作为。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "可能性强迫我去追求、去行动。\\n是可能性剥夺了我的自由！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_14"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你、你在说些什么……\\n为什么不能有所追求！？\\n可能性不就是希望吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "我不指望你能够理解我。\\n不……你永远都不可能理解我。\\n因为你觉得是可能性拯救了你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "那、那是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔托梅塞亚……\\n他释放了魔神之力吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "如果你想要了解我……\\n那我就告诉你一个好消息吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "能够吸收并操控魔神之力的人，\\n只有我一个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "除了我以外的“刻印之器”都不行。\\n哪怕是那个人的傀儡，\\n一旦吸收了魔神之力，意识就会被侵占。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "那是因为，\\n我是最为接近魔神……\\n接近黑暗魔力本质的意志。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "本质……\\n我记得黑暗魔力其实是\\n“起始之人”的愤怒……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "没错，是愤怒和憎恨。\\n对世界的愤怒和对可能性的憎恨\\n就是黑暗魔力的本质！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n既然你说你是可能性的证据，\\n那我就要否定你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "我要否定这世界的一切！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_26_04_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}